<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="a7May1917"><font color="red">7 May 1917</font>, <cite>Pound Letters</cite> (Ezra Pound to LR): Joyce is in hospital with small chance of doing much. I want however to be able to enlarge format WHEN his next novel is ready, and also to pay him at least &pound;50 for it.</div>
